Question 6

q6 <- function(k,df){
  if(k==1){
    fact <-  df %>% select_if(~(is.factor(.)&(nlevels(.)<4)))
    map(1:length(fact), function(x){map(1:length(fact), function(y){ggplot(fact,aes(x=fact[[x]], fill = fact[[y]]))+geom_bar()+labs(x=names(fact)[[x]],fill=names(fact)[[y]])})})
  } 
  else if(k==2){
    num <- df %>% select_if(~is.numeric(.))
    map(1:length(num), function(x){ggplot(num, aes(x=num[[x]])) + geom_density() + labs(x=names(num)[[x]])})
  }
  else if(k==3){
    fact = df %>% select_if(~(is.factor(.)&(nlevels(.)<4)))
    num <- df %>% select_if(~is.numeric(.))
    map(1:length(num), function(x){map(1:length(fact), function(y){ggplot(df, aes(x=num[[x]], color = fact[[y]])) + geom_density() + labs(x=names(num)[[x]], color=names(fact)[[y]])})})
  }
}
q6(3,titanic)

Question 7

titanic$PassengerId <- as.numeric(titanic$PassengerId)
q7 <- function(df){
  num <- df %>% select_if(~is.numeric(.)) 
  dataframe = data.frame("X1", "X2")
  map_df(1:length(num), function(x){map_df(1:length(num),function(y){data.frame('X1'=names(num)[x],'X2'= names(num)[y],'rsquare'= round(summary(lm(num[[x]]~num[[y]]))$r.square,4))})})
}
